e: to surround / to encircle / to corral

n: Scientific name: Rosa rugosa (CC-CEDICT '玫瑰'; Guoyu '玫瑰' 1; Wikipedia '玫瑰')

Sanskrit equivalent: pañcaskandha, Pāli: pañcakhandhā, Japanese: goun; the five skandhas are form 色, sensation 受, perception 想, volition 行, and consciousness 识 (FGDB '五蘊'; DJBT 'goun'; Tzu Chuang 2012; Nyanatiloka Thera 1980, 'khandha')
